<blockquote local-id=3D"e9fec234-5362-47f8-a1e5-2c887172ec71">
<p local-id=3D"3d7c57330ef1"><em>Note: The individual flow does not emit </=
em><code>person:completed</code><em> events, as there is only one person be=
ing verified.</em></p>
</blockquote>
